---
title: Cheesy Cheese Curd and Double Beef Burgers with Garlic-Rosemary Foil-Pouch Potatoes
description: Get ready to hit the grill with ooey-gooey cheesy burgers! Elevate your tastebuds with rosemary-studded patties topped with Canadian cheese curds and fig jam. An elegant side of garlic-grilled potatoes rounds off this long weekend winner!
